{"id":230853,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":6,"day":21}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"俄语周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"158","ytitle":"","mtitle":"美哉祖国","ftitle":"","authors":["朱纯","富强"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱纯　富强　译"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀着大地不熄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆红星的和平光芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有更自由的疆土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比之故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比祖国更美的，世界上没有!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们勇敢地征服自然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更新古老地土的面貌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们栽植森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更改河道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让沙漠上的园林开放灿烂的花苞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美吧，祖国——苏维埃的国家!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信守列宁和斯大林的真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把幸福与自由"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给各族人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你像史诗中的勇士样地刚强!&lt;img=516L070601&gt;"}]}